        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus domni <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/2137"
                            >Benedicti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">pape</rs> sede quinto sitque imperante <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130">Enrico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> in Italia vero anno quarto, die
                        detjmo mense ianuario, ind(itjone) prima, <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Ravenne</placeName>. Petimus a vobis domnus <persName
                            key="#Priests #Abbots" ref="#people/1582">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abb(as)</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">mon(asterii)</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Books #Rent_in_money #Plebs #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie qui vocatur in <placeName key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Books #Rent_in_money #Plebs #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/4179">Ponposa</placeName></orgName> uti nobis
                        press(entibus) in Christi nomine <persName><name ref="Sisilicus"
                                >Sisilicus</name></persName> petitore pro me et pro <persName><name
                                ref="Albitia">Albiza</name></persName> iugales mea seu filiis et
                        nepotibus meis per <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfiteouticario
                            ius</rs> a presenti die concedisti et largisti nobis rem iuris
                        suprascripto mon(asterio) vestro, idest omnes res et pertinentja vestra in
                        int(egro) quantascumque pertinet ad suprascripto mon(asterio) vestro in <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Price #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Books #Rent_in_money #Plebs #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2464"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Price #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Books #Rent_in_money #Plebs #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Lusirago seu in sorte de Mauro</placeName></geogName> in loco qui
                        ditjtur <placeName ref="#places/3587">Porto de Vetraria</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">satjonalibus</rs>,
                            <rs>arbustis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscatjonibus</rs> et <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venatjonibus</rs> et <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >ocupatjonibus</rs> suis et cum omnibus ad suprascripta res in int(egro)
                        pertinentibus, sit(as) in <rs key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3611">Sancte Marie qui vocatur
                            in Porto</orgName>, <rs key="#Confinia">interrafines</rs> de
                        suprascripta res: a primo latere <placeName key="#Confinia"
                            ref="#places/3589">Loiba</placeName>, a secundo latere <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Rivers" ref="#places/3588">Sandalo</placeName>, a tertjo
                        latere <placeName key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3590">Maurixini</placeName>,
                        a quarto latere <placeName key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3591"
                            >Remolago</placeName>. Dum nos superius nominatis petitoribus ea rem que
                        superius legitur abendum, tenendum, possidendum, defensandum et in omnibus
                        melliorandum; et vos et vestris sucessoribus nobis nostrisque filiis et
                        nepotibus ipsa rem que superius legitur ab omni persona ominum defensare et
                        auctoriare promisisti; et ex nostris propriis expensis seu laboribus
                        nichilque vobis vestrisque sucessoribus nisi inferius adfixam pensione
                        reputantes. Prestantibus quoque nobis nostrisque filiis et nepotibus
                        singulis quibusque annis omni martji mense infra ind(itjonem), pro ipsa rem
                        que superius legitur, idest <rs key="#Rent_in_money">in arientum den(ario)s
                            duos tantum</rs> pensio ut dictum est persolvatur. Pro eo quia exinde
                        accepisti de manibus meis pro me et pro suprascripta coniux mea manibus
                        vestris in pressentjam testium, qui ic subter scripturi sunt, caltjarii
                        nomine, idest <rs key="#Books">libro</rs> uno pro <rs key="#Price"
                            >denariorum sollidos viginti</rs> et pro unoquemque sollidos ana
                        den(ario)s duodetjm. Ita et post transitum nostrorumque filiorum et nepotum,
                        munimine expleto quandoque Domino sue sancte magestatis placuerit, tunc
                        ipsas res que superius legitur cultas, laborata, defensata et in omnibus
                        melliorata vel quicquid a nobis inibi aditum melioratumque fuerit ad ius
                        dominiumque mon(asterio) vestro cuius est ius et proprietas modis omnibus
                        revertatur. Promitto propterea nonnullis diebus nullisque temporibus vite
                        nostre vos autem vel vestris successoribus testus huius paginam enfiteossis
                        violabimus set inviolabiliter observabimus et si ec p[eti]tjo mea nobis in
                        vobis facta minime valere nequiverint, tunc daturos nos promittimus
                        nostrisque filiis et nepotibus vobis vestrisque sucessoribus ANTE OMNE litis
                        initjum aut interpell(atjonem) pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri obtimi
                            untjas quatuor</rs> et post pene solutjone manead petitjone in sua
                        firmitatem. Quam vero petitjone <persName key="#Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Ioh(anne)s</name></persName> in Dei nomine <rs
                            key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> Rav(ennas) scribendum rogavi, in qua et
                        ego subter manus mea subscripsi et rogatis testibus illam tibi in eorum
                        pressentja tradidit, sub die et mense et ind(itjone) suprascripta prima,
                        RAVENNE. Sisilicus in hac peticione ut s(u)p(erius) l(egitur) a me facta
                        s(ub)s(cripsi).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
